author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cutera Q4 Revenue $47.6 Million
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Cutera Inc:
* CUTERA REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER AND FULL YEAR 2017 RECORD REVENUE AND FINANCIAL RESULTS
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.57 * Q4 REVENUE $47.6 MILLION * SEES FY 2018 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.03 TO $1.11
* SEES FY 2018 REVENUE UP 18 TO 20 PERCENT * SEES FY 2018 REVENUE $178 MILLION TO $181 MILLION * Q4 NON-GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.42
* ‍EXPECT 2018 REVENUE TO BE IN RANGE OF $178 MILLION TO $181 MILLION​
* CUTERA - ‍IN Q4 OF 2017, CO RECORDED AN INCOME TAX BENEFIT OF $18.2 MILLION RESULTING FROM RECENT TAX REFORM
* SEES ‍2018 GROSS MARGIN IS EXPECTED TO BE IN RANGE OF 57% TO 58%​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
